Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_mac_credit_cnt2

This register contains the number of credits for the MAC port FIFOs (for MACs 2 and 3) used by the SLI. This value must be set before S2M traffic flow starts. A write to this register causes the credit counts in the SLI for the MAC ports to be reset to the value in this register.
